ReverbNation has a temporary assignment open for a driven and experienced <strong>Technical Recruiter/HR Generalist</strong>. Our Recruiter/HR Generalist will be responsible for <strong>full lifecycle recruitment</strong> of corporate positions and will report to our CFO. The successful candidate will not only be a killer recruiter but also be able to manage other areas of the HR function and contribute to other various projects supporting the management team. Assignments and responsibilities may also include employee on-boarding, project management, vendor management, documentation/filing, process improvement, planning company activities, etc.</p>
<p>
